		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I am working on (once again) a Pong game, this time on the Gameboy. So far a ball is on the screen and moves to the top left.<br /><br />...On BGB, that is. When testing on my flashcart, the code gives the following results:<br /><br />GBPocket: Works.<br />GBC: Blank screen.<br />GBA SP: Blank screen.<br /><br />Anyone have any idea as to why?

		
